headline: Lucid Inks New Partnership With VITALExam: Stock to Gain?
summary: LUCD collaborates with VITALExam to enhance access to the EsoGuard Esophageal DNA Test. The partnership launches a fully contracted testing event for Tuscaloosa firefighters.
